article.headline: Drake 71, Austin Peay 54
article.story: DES MOINES, Iowa -- Josh Parker scored 19 points, Jonathan Cox had 14 points and 14 rebounds and Drake beat Austin Peay 71-54 on Saturday night. Josh Young added 11 points and Craig Stanley 10 to help the Bulldogs (17-12) clinch their third straight winning season for the first time since 1978-81. Drake Reed had 22 points and five rebounds and Wes Channels scored 12 for the Governors (15-12).
